#==============================================================================
# FUNCTION DEFINITION: 'interleave_lists'
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Purpose: This defines a reusable block of code that can be called later.
# Function name: 'interleave_lists' - follows snake_case convention (lowercase with underscores).
